<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1693</hymn_number>
<author>Marco Prezioso</author>
<title>Lord give me a new song</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lord, give me a new song
 To start a new day
 To start a new life
 Nothing but Your wondrous grace
 Made me your son
 Makes me feel alive

[V2]
 In me, all the time
 Your Spirit lives
 In me, oh yeah!
 Nobody and nothing
 Can stop me to praise

[V3]
 I shout and my voice from my heart
 Reaches out Your throne, Lord
 Just to let You know:
 I love You!</lyrics>
</song>